00:41:42,590 --> 00:41:43,850
he can't finish it all.

852
00:41:44,390 --> 00:41:45,550
We'll start small.

853
00:41:45,590 --> 00:41:48,390
We can use existing programming templates.

854
00:41:48,430 --> 00:41:49,470
Once we have money,

855
00:41:49,470 --> 00:41:50,620
then we can spend it

856
00:41:50,670 --> 00:41:52,590
to hire programmers from outside.

857
00:41:52,590 --> 00:41:54,590
There are virtual servers online,

858
00:41:54,610 --> 00:41:57,850
but if you want to guarantee storage and internet speed,

859
00:41:57,950 --> 00:41:59,840
you must rent a dedicated server.

860
00:42:00,470 --> 00:42:01,870
Then let's go to Beijing.

861
00:42:02,110 --> 00:42:03,770
I've already talked to my dad.

862
00:42:04,720 --> 00:42:05,650
He didn't agree.

863
00:42:06,110 --> 00:42:08,040
But he didn't object either.

864
00:42:10,230 --> 00:42:11,670
What's the use of your dad agreeing?

865
00:42:11,670 --> 00:42:13,560
You won't get your mom's approval.

866
00:42:13,560 --> 00:42:15,290
We have to try, right?

867
00:42:15,670 --> 00:42:16,590
I don't believe

868
00:42:16,590 --> 00:42:18,310
When Bill Gates dropped out from Harvard,

869
00:42:18,310 --> 00:42:19,370
his mom could agree.

870
00:42:19,370 --> 00:42:20,250
To do great things,

871
00:42:20,250 --> 00:42:21,840
we must all forge ahead through difficulties.

872
00:42:21,840 --> 00:42:23,550
Anyway, I must do this.

873
00:42:33,700 --> 00:42:35,090
If we really can make money,

874
00:42:35,090 --> 00:42:36,550
how do you want to spend it?

875
00:42:37,070 --> 00:42:38,260
First, pay off debts.

876
00:42:38,260 --> 00:42:39,710
I haven't finished paying off

877
00:42:39,710 --> 00:42:40,870
my mom's debts yet.

878
00:42:43,280 --> 00:42:44,710
I plan to buy a phone,

879
00:42:44,750 --> 00:42:46,020
the latest model.

880
00:42:46,040 --> 00:42:46,790
Then,

881
00:42:46,810 --> 00:42:49,470
I'll make calls in front of Xie Wanghe every day.

882
00:42:50,080 --> 00:42:51,610
Hello, darling,

883
00:42:51,630 --> 00:42:53,230
have you been missing me these days?

884
00:42:53,230 --> 00:42:54,760
Which darling?

885
00:42:55,430 --> 00:42:56,030
It doesn't matter.

886
00:42:56,030 --> 00:42:58,470
The point is to make him see my new phone.

887
00:42:58,550 --> 00:42:59,750
I'll make him so jealous.

